    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a superlative example of the E46 M3, a vehicle that represents the high-water mark of naturally aspirated BMW engineering. This specimen features the S54 B32 power plant, delivering a linear torque curve and an 8,000 RPM redline through six individual throttle bodies. The double-VANOS timing system has been meticulously overhauled to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. The chassis integrity is verified, including comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension geometry utilizing OEM bushings to maintain original turn-in characteristics. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock. The exterior retains its factory-applied clear coat with no evidence of thermal cycling or environmental degradation. Mechanically synchronized and aesthetically flawless, this is a turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
